94">在 2023 年 BET 颁奖典礼上与 Quavo 一起表演向 Takeoff 致敬“净化了他的灵魂”</a> 。这是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/migos-quavo-and-offset-perform-together-for-first-time-since-takeoffs-death-at-2023-bet-awards-3461544">自 Takeoff 去世后两人首次一起表演</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/quavo-confirms-release-date-and-details-for-new-album-rocket-power-3471924">Quavo 确认新专辑《Rocket Power》发行日期和详细信息的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
马蒂·希利 (Matty Healy) 在音乐节期间批评政府和反 LGBTQ 法律后，《1975》被禁止在马来西亚演出https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-banned-from-malaysia-good-vibes-festival-cancelled-matty-healy-3471893?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-1975-banned-from-malaysia-good-vibes-festival-cancelled-matty-healyWill Richards Sat, 22 Jul 2023 11:14:29 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3471893 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="1975年" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>当局下令取消剩余两天的好氛围节，马来西亚通讯部长表示“不会与任何挑战、贬低或违反马来西亚法律的政党妥协”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-banned-from-malaysia-good-vibes-festival-cancelled-matty-healy-3471893">马蒂·希利 (Matty Healy) 在音乐节期间批评政府和反 LGBTQ 法律后，The 1975 被禁止在马来西亚演出，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="1975年" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">The 1975</a>的 Matty Healy 在头条节目中批评该国的反 LGBTQ 法律及其政府后，马来西亚 Good Vibes Festival 的剩余活动已被取消。</p><p>据马来西亚负责批准外国艺术家拍摄和表演申请的官方机构称，该乐队也被禁止在马来西亚演出。</p><p>在周五晚上（7 月 21 日）的头条新闻中，希利<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-good-vibes-festival-malaysia-set-cut-short-matty-healy-criticises-anti-lgbtq-laws-kiss-bassist-3471738">大声疾呼该国的反同性恋法律，批评其政府，并在舞台上亲吻了贝斯手罗斯·麦克唐纳</a>。 “我不认为邀请 1975 年来到一个国家，然后告诉我们可以和谁发生性关系，”希利对人群说。 1975 年的演出被缩短，乐队在希利发言后离开舞台，唱了两首歌。</p><p>马来西亚法律将同性之间的性行为定为犯罪，其<a href="https://www.ilo.org/dyn/natlex/docs/ELECTRONIC/61339/117909/F1085941047/MYS61339%202015.pdf">刑法</a>将“违反自然秩序的性交”和“严重猥亵”行为定为犯罪。</p><p>事件发生后，吉隆坡音乐节发表官方声明称，The 1975 的演出因“不遵守当地演出指南”而被缩短，但音乐节剩余两天将继续进行，持有周五门票的歌迷可以免费参加这两天的其中一天。</p><p>然而，周六下午，马来西亚通讯部长在社交媒体上表示，他已与音乐节组织者Future Sound Asia会面，并下令取消音乐节的其余活动。 Good Vibes Festival 随后发表了一份官方声明，确认其取消，并表示该决定是在 The 1975 片场发生事件后做出的。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="in" dir="ltr"> Saya telah memanggil penganjur Festival Good Vibes 2023 iaitu Future Sound Asia，苏苏兰·阿克西和肯亚塔·比亚达布·扬·迪帕默坎·奥莱·阿蒂斯·达里·英国“The 1975”迪雪邦马拉姆·塔迪。 <a href="https://t.co/0X0xjnAmVJ">pic.twitter.com/0X0xjnAmVJ</a></p><p> — 法赫米·法齐尔<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f1f2-1f1fe.png" alt="🇲🇾" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> （@fahmi_fadzil） <a href="https://twitter.com/fahmi_fadzil/status/1682621664306274305?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 7 月 22 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>它在 Instagram 上写道：“由于来自 The 1975 乐队的英国艺术家马蒂·希利 (Matty Healy) 的有争议的行为和言论，计划于今天和明天举行的 Good Vibes Festival 剩余日程被取消，我们深感遗憾。</p><p> “该决定符合通信和数字部于 2023 年 7 月 22 日下午 1 点 20 分发布的立即取消指令。该部强调其对任何挑战、嘲笑或违反马来西亚法律的政党的坚定立场。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cu_cQPry_wN/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M54